name: Business service
lookup_fields: Name, service_classification, name_1, parent_1, assignment_group, support_group, u_vendor_support_group
lookup_hidden_fields: Name, service_classification, parent_1, assignment_group, support_group, u_vendor_support_group
lookup_filter:
Filter 1 - (Match All) :
- service_classification EQUAL_TO Business Service-Value

name: Technical service
lookup_fields: Name, name_1, service_classification, parent_1, support_group, u_vendor_support_group, assignment_group
lookup_hidden_fields: Name, service_classification, parent_1, support_group, u_vendor_support_group, assignment_group
lookup_filter:
Filter 1 - (Match All) :
- service_classification EQUAL_TO Technical Service-Value
- parent_1 EQUAL_TO Business_Service_Parent-Field

name: Priority
formula: if(Impact="1 - High"&&Urgency="1 - High","1 - Critical",if(Impact="1 - High"&&Urgency="2 - Medium","2 - High",if(Impact="1 - High"&&Urgency="3 - Low","3 - Minor",if(Impact="2 - Medium"&&Urgency="1 - High","2 - High",if(Impact="2 - Medium"&&Urgency="2 - Medium","3 - Minor",if(Impact="2 - Medium"&&Urgency="3 - Low","4 - Low",if(Impact="3 - Low"&&Urgency="1 - High","3 - Minor",if(Impact="3 - Low"&&Urgency="2 - Medium","4 - Low",if(Impact="3 - Low"&&Urgency="3 - Low","5 - Planning","")))))))))

name: Assignment group
visibility_rules:
Field visibility rules - Match All: 
- Choosing_Assignment_group_L2 EQUAL_TO false-Value
lookup_filter:
Filter 1 - (Match All) :
- name_1 EQUAL_TO BS_Assign-Field
- name_1 EQUAL_TO TEC_Assign-Field

name: Assigned to
lookup_filter:
Filter 1 - (Match All) :
- usr_group CONTAINS Assignment_Group_Name-Field
- usr_group CONTAINS Assignment_Group_Name_L2-Field

name: Assignment group L2
visibility_rules:
Field visibility rules - Match All: 
- Choosing_Assignment_group_L2 EQUAL_TO true-Value
lookup_filter:
Filter 1 - (Match All) :
- name_1 EQUAL_TO BS_Vendor_Support-Field
- name_1 EQUAL_TO TEC_Support-Field

name: Pending Change
visibility_rules:
Field visibility rules - Match All: 
- Take_Val EQUAL_TO Show-Value

name: Closed/Resolved
visibility_rules:
Field visibility rules - Match All: 
- Take_Val EQUAL_TO Show-Value
- Take EQUAL_TO true-Value

name: Activity Control Validation 1
visibility_rules:
Field visibility rules - Match All: 
- Activity_Control_Validation EQUAL_TO DNS-Value

name: Vendor Contact (L3)
visibility_rules:
Field visibility rules - Match All: 
- Choosing_Assignment_group_L2 EQUAL_TO true-Value

name: PIC Contact (Non Kissflow User)
visibility_rules:
Field visibility rules - Match All: 
- Non_Kissflow_User EQUAL_TO true-Value

name: TASK SLA RESOLUTION
lookup_filter:
Filter 1 - (Match All) :
- Table EQUAL_TO problem-Value
- Target EQUAL_TO Resolution-Value
- Priority CONTAINS Priority_Text-Field
- Assignment_Group CONTAINS Assignment_Group_Text-Field
- Service_Type EQUAL_TO Service_Type_Text-Field
